      <title>Nvidia 同意收购软件初创公司 Shoreline</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-agrees-deal-to-buy-software-startup-shoreline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，Nvidia Corp. 已同意收购由前亚马逊网络服务高管创建的软件开发初创公司 Shoreline.io。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-agrees-deal-to-buy-software-startup-shoreline</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 18:45:19 GMT</pubDate>
