    <item>
      <title>人工智能生成的原住民艺术促使加拿大 Telus 制定新的道德规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/ai-generated-indigenous-art-spurs-new-ethics-rules-at-canada-s-telus-t</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大电信公司 Telus Corp. 承诺不会使用人工智能制作或复制土著艺术，此前一些社区抱怨该技术盗用了他们的文化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/ai-generated-indigenous-art-spurs-new-ethics-rules-at-canada-s-telus-t</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 18:14:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国寻求盟友帮助遏制中国人工智能内存芯片发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-to-seek-curbs-on-asml-tokyo-electron-support-for-china-s-ai-memory-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名美国高级官员即将访问日本和荷兰，要求两国对中国半导体行业增加新的限制，包括其生产人工智能所需的高端存储芯片的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-to-seek-curbs-on-asml-tokyo-electron-support-for-china-s-ai-memory-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 16:38:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>牛市预期 Nvidia 估值接近 5 万亿美元，股价延续涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-nvda-extends-rally-as-bull-sees-valuation-nearing-5-trillion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 的股价在过去一年中飙升了 200% 以上，一位最看好的分析师预测，这家半导体巨头将延续涨势，在未来一年将其市值推高至近 5 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-nvda-extends-rally-as-bull-sees-valuation-nearing-5-trillion</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:45:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>任天堂在下一代 Switch 游戏发布前宣布推出新版塞尔达和马里奥游戏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nintendo-announces-new-zelda-mario-games-ahead-of-next-switch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[任天堂有限公司宣布，将于今年晚些时候在 Switch 上发布几款新游戏，预计新游戏机将于 2025 年初推出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nintendo-announces-new-zelda-mario-games-ahead-of-next-switch</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:29:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>芯片制造商争相供应水源，台湾中鼎计划建设水厂</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/taiwan-s-ctci-plans-water-plant-as-chipmakers-clamor-for-supply</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着芯片制造商的需求猛增，台湾中鼎科技股份有限公司及其合作伙伴将开发和运营一座价值 5.08 亿欧元（5.45 亿美元）的海水淡化厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/taiwan-s-ctci-plans-water-plant-as-chipmakers-clamor-for-supply</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:08:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国立法者希望禁止芯片法案获胜者使用中国工具</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/lawmakers-look-to-bar-chips-act-winners-from-using-chinese-tools</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国立法者希望阻止获得联邦芯片制造基金的公司在政府支持的工厂使用中国制造的设备，这是限制北京对国内芯片生产影响的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/lawmakers-look-to-bar-chips-act-winners-from-using-chinese-tools</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 15:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pritzker 选择 IBM 和 Discover 竞购联邦量子基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/pritzker-taps-ibm-discover-in-bid-for-federal-quantum-funds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州州长 J.B. Pritzker 已向包括国际商业机器公司和 Discover Financial Services 在内的财团寻求帮助，以赢得联邦资金来开发量子技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/pritzker-taps-ibm-discover-in-bid-for-federal-quantum-funds</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 14:50:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Nvidia 内部人士趁股价上涨获利，股票销售额突破 7 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-nvda-insiders-cash-in-on-rally-as-share-sales-top-700-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场对英伟达芯片的需求持续旺盛，该公司股价不断攀升至历史最高水平，今年以来，该公司内部人士已出售了价值超过 7 亿美元的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/nvidia-nvda-insiders-cash-in-on-rally-as-share-sales-top-700-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 11:15:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国与印度访问期间重启敏感技术谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-india-resume-talks-on-sensitive-technologies-during-visit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美印两国国家安全顾问在新德里举行会晤后发表的联合声明表示，两国在芯片、人工智能和太空等战略领域的合作仍在继续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/us-india-resume-talks-on-sensitive-technologies-during-visit</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 06:37:09 GMT</pubDate>
